concept.title: IEC 61850 Reality Prime AC UPS List

othermeta.name: title
othermeta.content: IEC 61850 Reality Modular AC UPS List CPT DD00544734

othermeta.name: shortdesc
othermeta.content: Component and IEC 61850 mapping list for Reality modular AC UPS systems, including bypass and inverter modules.

conbody.p: The default logical device (LD) for all IEC tags for Reality Prime AC UPS is “i61PRIMEACUPS_LD1”.

The IEC tag path format is LN$FC$DO$DA.
Logical node (LN)
Functional constraint (FC)
Data object (DO)
Data attribute (DA)
conbody.note: The Data Type for Status is Boolean and for Analog is UINT32 (2).
